There is a single real word that takes three hours to read outloud. A babysitter made me listen to it as punishment.

Do you have the time,

To listen to me whine, 

About nothing and everything all at once?

I am one of those, 

Melodramatic fools, 

Neurotic to the bone no doubt about it.

I forgot the rest of the song
